; Graphics, animation frame 1 of 4 -- masks for Pogo (frames 2-4 are
; gfx_c26e/gfx_c2e6/gfx_c35e, each an independent block).
; .
; NOT a raw 1bpp raster -- these bytes only become real pixels after
; calc_sprite_shift/expand_sprite_b's self-modifying decode (see
; patch_expand_masks, $8E48). Reading this block directly as a bitmap produces
; garbage; a UDG array macro cannot render it.
; .
; Verified by emulation (decode_sprite.py, real Z80 core, self-mod masks forced
