;
; Used by the routine at #R$FE5C.
;
; .
;
; Read one byte from tape with the custom turbo edge-timing loop (ULA EAR bit
; via IN ($FE), border feedback via OUT ($FE)).
; .
; Accumulates 8 bits CY=success, NC=load error/abort.
